The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 Tip for Dravid: Shun Team Somnath model 

 New Delhi, March 1: Armchair critics can be ignored, but today Team India had advice from the Chair itself.

 The Lok Sabha Speaker said that if India wants to win the World Cup, it must avoid behaving like the countries unruly parliamentarians, says our special correspondent.

 Let us convey our best wishes to the team, Somnath Chatterjee told the House.

 Then, seeing the Sam- ajwadi Party din over the apex court order for a CBI probe into Mulayam Singh Yadavs wealth, he added: Let the players not follow us. 




